high_descs: Walk slightly forward to the sink.
Pick up the egg from the sink basin.
Turn around and walk across the room to the refrigerator.
Put the egg in the refrigerator for a few seconds, then take it out and close the refrigerator.
Turn around and walk back to the sink.
Put the egg back into the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled egg into a sink basin.

high_descs: Look down in the kitchen sink.
Pick up the egg that is in the sink.
Turn right, walk to the end of the cabinetry, then turn right and walk up to the fridge.
Chill the egg in the fridge before taking it out and closing the door.
Turn to the right, walk to the oven, then turn right and walk up to the kitchen sink.
Place the egg in the kitchen sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a chilled egg to the kitchen sink.

high_descs: Pick up the egg in the sink.
Turn around, bring the egg to the fridge, left of the counter.
Chill the egg in the fridge.
Take the chilled egg back to the sink behind you.
Put the chilled egg in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled egg in the sink.
